{"tid":1016705,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網民熱話：獲贈$100睇醫生 女生網上尋「大俠」","createTime":"2019-02-11T02:10:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T03:12:26.000Z","uid":56881,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d74c56fedfe4f4098314bc8c3e6b880a31a0c048","tid":1016705,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T02:10:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1-%E7%8D%B2%E8%B4%88-100%E7%9D%87%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F-%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E5%B0%8B-%E5%A4%A7%E4%BF%A0-103816462.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25A9%25B1-%25E7%258D%25B2%25E8%25B4%2588-100%25E7%259D%2587%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F-%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%25B0%258B-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BF%25A0-103816462.html&d=rjg6%2Bw4p6Mv2XY9C6AOo54yfatP4vaZW2FmQrzE7DSA%3D&h=aa44bb72\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1-%E7%8D%B2%E8%B4%88-100%E7%9D%87%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F-%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E5%B0%8B-%E5%A4%A7%E4%BF%A0-103816462.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/pCYpB.FBHYQUZd_OykA4BA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/onccinstantnews.com/64e12116e2d9dcad9ab29bd2087e7aee\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FpCYpB.FBHYQUZd_OykA4BA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F64e12116e2d9dcad9ab29bd2087e7aee&h=320626ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=rjg6%2Bw4p6Mv2XY9C6AOo54yfatP4vaZW2FmQrzE7DSA%3D&h=3c6e182d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】助人為快樂之本，路見不平拔刀相助而不望回報者，大有人在。昨日（9日）有網民在社交平台上尋人，不過尋找的並非親友，而是一位陌生人，一位不留名的好心「大俠」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民Ellen Lam在Facebook群組「Tai Po 大埔」上發文尋人，事緣在年三十晚（2月4日）中午，發文者趁醫生收爐前趕往看病，到拿藥時才發現身上現金不夠，故到附近櫃員機提款。或許正值新年前夕，太多人排隊撳機，最後一名年約50歲的男子把櫃員機剩餘的紙幣提走後，便向身後隊伍表示：「（櫃員機）冇無晒錢嚕。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n心急的發文者，當時決定向該名男子求助：「可唔可以借$100畀我？」男子聞言後竟爽快地從剛提取的現金中，抽出1張港幣100元，笑着表示：「拎去，畀你嘅」。雖已不斷要求對方留下聯絡方法，方便在取藥後到其他地方撳機還錢，惟對方卻堅拒，「最後仲秒速同老婆拖手走咗。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發文者表示，其實當時可以到超市或便利店購物提款，不過因為「病到溫溫燉燉」想不起，現時病情好轉，希望透過網上尋人，向好心人道謝及還錢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不少網民分享貼文，也有人祝福好心人有好報。另有網民建議把捐錢，繼續幫助下一個有需要的人，讓心意傳承。最後事主決定向動物機構捐款港幣500元，但仍希望能夠找到好心人還錢及道謝。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好人一生平安"},{"pid":"77eea34b597aa6542a2f50927db65ec80e32aaad","tid":1016705,"uid":27591,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T02:21:33.000Z","msg":"「最後仲秒速同老婆拖手走咗。」<br />\n<br />\n佢老婆唔係度就一早比左你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90349fe210dfe925d864c17f0c5eb95c31f7648e","tid":1016705,"uid":35815,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T02:22:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"00099445435280e1b42bbfc27a83c94a1db68878","tid":1016705,"uid":166792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T02:28:16.000Z","msg":"比多張搭車啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ff503feca34060c7e16dc8a7036cab27662d65","tid":1016705,"uid":40052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T02:35:50.000Z","msg":"唔知幾時開始 已經自動將哩d新聞當騙案咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af747808b3b92de1de07c50990553c1306a749ea","tid":1016705,"uid":189243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T03:12:26.000Z","msg":"好人好事，這是以前香港每日都有幾會發生嘅事。<br />\n依家你會諗係咪大陸人揾食，令好心人卻步。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]